the performance of an electric motor. If the issue is fault related press the Clear Faults button located in the Troubleshooting Tab. All other issues must
be dealt with by removing the left motor controller and running a diagnostic test."
        android:textColor="@android:color/white"
        android:textSize="20sp"
        app:layout_constraintBottom_toBottomOf="parent"
        app:layout_constraintEnd_toEndOf="parent"
