    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/fixAccelerator"
        android:layout_width="630dp"
        android:layout_height="280dp"
        android:elevation="11dp"
        android:text="Accelerator Pedal Troubleshooting: The accelerator is also known as gas pedal. It is the pedal located on the floor on the far-right.
This pedal controls the amount of torque being sent to the motor controllers and thereby controls the speed of the vehicle. If the issue is hardware related then the
accelerator must be removed and further diagnosed. Make sure all wires are properly connected. If the issue is software related then the a diagnostics test must ba
done on code of the the back Teensy unit."
        android:textColor="@android:color/white"
        android:textSize="20sp"
        app:layout_constraintBottom_toBottomOf="parent"
        app:layout_constraintEnd_toEndOf="parent"
        app:layout_constraintHorizontal_bias="0.495"
